555 Timer Circuit Connection
For Astable Connection
🔹 Power Connections
Pin 8 (VCC) → +9V
Pin 1 (GND) → Ground
🔹 Reset Pin
Pin 4 (RESET) → +9V
🔹 Control Voltage
Pin 5 → Capacitor (C2 = 10nF) → Ground
🔹 Timing Network (MAIN PART)
Pin 7 (DISCHARGE) → R1 → +9V
Pin 7 → R2 → Pin 6
Pin 6 (THRESHOLD) → Pin 2 (TRIGGER) (connect together)
Pin 6/2 → Capacitor (C1) → Ground
🔹 Output (LED)
Pin 3 (OUTPUT) → LED → Resistor → Ground


 
For Monostable Circuit Connection
🔹 Power
Pin 8 → +VCC
Pin 1 → GND
🔹 Reset
Pin 4 → +VCC
🔹 Control Voltage
Pin 5 → 10nF capacitor → GND
🔹 Trigger Input
Pin 2 → Push button → GND
Pin 2 → Pull-up resistor → +VCC
🔹 Timing Circuit
Pin 6 → Node
Pin 7 → Node

Node → Resistor → +VCC
Node → Capacitor → GND

🔹 Output
Pin 3 → LED → Resistor → GND
